      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 9 What's Doing column about reopening of Savoy Hotel in Florence; building's first occupant, for which it was built in 1893, was Italian and Jewish but not an Israelite (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A chart on July 9 with the What Doing column, about Philadelphia, misstated the fare for a ride downtown from the airport. It is $20, not $22.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
